  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You raise your religious symbol and create a blinding flash of light. Each creature in the area must attempt a Fortitude save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.TkIyaNPgTZFBCCuh]{Dazzled} for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.XgEqL1kFApUbl5Z2]{Blinded} for 1 round and Dazzled for 1 minute. The creature can spend an Interact action rubbing its eyes to end the Blinded condition.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is Blinded for 1 round and Dazzled for 1 hour.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (3rd)</strong> The area increases to a 30-foot cone.</p>"
